cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.GR 

This paper proposes a novel data augmentation technique applied to Salient Object Detection (SOD) using deep neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves image processing, which could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper involves the evaluation of the proposed method using metrics, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.GR (Graphics).
